  +ComponentCard({title:'Basic Modal'}).my-4
    button.btn.btn-primary(type='button' data-bs-toggle='modal' data-bs-target='#exampleModal')
      | Launch basic modal
    #exampleModal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1' aria-labelledby='exampleModalLabel' aria-hidden='true')
      .modal-dialog
        .modal-content
          .modal-header
            h5#exampleModalLabel.modal-title Modal title
            button.btn.p-1(type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' aria-label='Close')
              span.fas.fa-times.fs--1
          .modal-body
            p.text-700.lh-lg.mb-0 This is a static modal example (meaning its position and display have been overridden). Included are the modal header, modal body (required for padding), and modal footer (optional). 
          .modal-footer
            button.btn.btn-primary(type='button') Okay
            button.btn.btn-outline-primary(type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal') Cancel

